Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Proposition 13
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bs1p
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 26 May 1978
Californians to vote on Proposition 13 change to local taxation. Bakke case comes to court. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less